# Getting Started

To get started with contributing, please follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository on GitHub.
2. Install the necessary dependencies by running `npx projen`.

## Local deployment

1. Change the endpoint in App.tsx to point to http://localhost:4000/trpc (Line 10)
2. Start the backend server

```
tsx backend/src/server-stub.ts
```

3. Start the frontend, in the front end folder:

```
cd frontend
yarn dev
```

## AWS deployment

1.  Bootstrap the account you are going to use:

```
npx cdk bootstrap aws://ACCOUNT_ID/eu-west-1
```

2. Deploy the application

```
yarn cdk deploy
```
